    <Self::Storage as Storage>::Elem: 'a = Iter<'a, <<&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Storage as Storage>::Elem, <&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Dimensionality>

where
    Self: 'a,

    Self: 'a,
    D2: Dimensionality,
    O2: Order = ArrayBase<<<&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Storage as Storage>::Cow<'a>, D2, O2>

type Owned = ArrayBase<<<&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Storage as Storage>::Owned, <&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Dimensionality, <&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Order>

where
    Self: 'a = ArrayBase<<<&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Storage as Storage>::View<'a>, <&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Dimensionality, <&ArrayBase<S, D, O> as NDArray>::Order>

    Self: 'a,
